<div id="wrapper">
  <h1>Dice Game</h1>

  <h2>Welcome.</h2>

  <p>Here are the rules:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Roll the dice to start the game.</li>
    <li>If your first roll is a 7 or 11, you win.</li>
    <li>If your first roll is a 2, 3, or 12, you lose.</li>
    <li>Anything else becomes your <i>goal</i>.  Roll your goal again before rolling a 7 and you win.  Roll a 7 instead of your goal you lose.</li>
  </ul>

  <button onclick="location.href='/start'">Roll to start the game!</button>
  <!-- <% button_to "Roll to start the game!", {action: "start"} %> -->

 </div>
